title: WoW Unleashed Burning Crusade 2.4.3
description:
World of Warcraft Unleashed - The Burning Crusade

We bring you back the old nostalgic moments of one of the greatest Expansions in the history of World of Warcraft.

Enjoy once again The Burning Crusade, just as it once was on Retail.
Limited to 5000 players (whick is more than Retail).

XP Rates: x5
Drop Common: x10
Drop Uncommon: x10
Drop Rare: x5
Drop Epic: x2
Drop Gold: x5


With a massive community and forum you will get any help that you need from our fellow players and Game Masters. Come and enjoy our server and experience exclusive events and a lot more!
